summary:
This is just an ordinary follower, I made based on my own Viking persona (I do Viking Re-enactment)
He is a Nord and has his own personal sword named Mjolnir. Oh yeah, You can find him in the Four Shields Taven in Dragons Bridge. :) My first mod.
